        <p>A safe, modern, and spiritual environment for the leaders of tomorrow.</p>
        <a href="#primary" style="background:var(--ethiopia-gold); padding:15px 40px; color:#000; font-weight:800; border-radius:50px; text-decoration:none;">Explore Facilities</a>
    </header>

    <div class="ethio-spirit">
        <div class="green"></div><div class="yellow"></div><div class="red"></div>
    </div>

